    <LyceumGovAOLReleaseDir>$(ReleaseDir)\LyceumGovAOL</LyceumGovAOLReleaseDir>
    <LyceumGovDOLReleaseDir>$(ReleaseDir)\LyceumGovDOL</LyceumGovDOLReleaseDir>
    <ProcessoSeletivoAlunoReleaseDir>$(ReleaseDir)\ProcessoSeletivoAluno</ProcessoSeletivoAlunoReleaseDir>
